{"tid":440032,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[破紀錄]  9歲 Celine 譚芷昀香港紅館演唱會","createTime":"2017-10-18T11:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T00:37:22.000Z","uid":82845,"like":23,"dislike":1329,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"3c928fd8639f4d4ff6cfd81573fed85cbc12ef82","tid":440032,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:28:47.000Z","msg":"Celine 譚芷昀香港演唱會<br />\n<br />\n香港體育館 (紅館) 》香港紅磡暢運道9號<br />\n2017年12月1日 ‑ 2018年3月31日 (每日)<br />\n詳細日期有待公佈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pmchollywoodlife.files.wordpress.com/2017/08/laverne-cox-golden-buzzer-agt-ftr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpmchollywoodlife.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F08%2Flaverne-cox-golden-buzzer-agt-ftr.jpg&h=2ede5eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係得9歲嘅香港小巨肺Celine譚芷昀出戰《全美一叮》(America's Got Talent)，喺最新一集節目中拎到Golden Buzzer直送入半準決賽。<br />\n<br />\n人仔細細嘅Celine仲係小學生，但其實已經簽咗HMV，腦細細蕭生話:「今年年底或者出年年初可以去紅館開一個慈善演唱會。」<br />\n<br />\n喂阿哥！巨肺GEM都要20歲先開紅館喎，你有冇快成咁呢～ 網民對Celine評價兩極，Anyway，一位港產可愛小妹妹唱歌唱到AGT拎Golden Buzzer，點都係港人之光丫～你話是咪先～<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://timable.com/zh-hk/event/1483822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimable.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fevent%2F1483822&d=CYNFZRFoNhlE14fxwxRrKjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2226ed85\" target=\"_blank\">http://timable.com/zh-hk/event/1483822</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b00143b17e6ab3b7bb431dba6663d24bd7f6a05","tid":440032,"uid":58583,"like":314,"dislike":1,"score":313,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"唱足4個月"},{"pid":"1254424f8014e19829caed7fe25743736cf5646d","tid":440032,"uid":65144,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"so happy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210d8a52d64d3abf6e47b971334b1133db7ebfba","tid":440032,"uid":21423,"like":286,"dislike":4,"score":282,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"